criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Living in the catchment area of one of the 20 outpatient therapeutic program site
             participating in this cluster randomized trial;

          -  6-59 months of age;

          -  Weight for Height Zscore <-3 SD (WHO Growth Standards 2006) and/or Mid-Upper Arm
             Circumference <115mm and/or with bilateral edema;

          -  No major clinical complications;

          -  Positive appetite test;

          -  Accept to participate at the study.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Not living in the catchment area of the outpatient therapeutic program site of the
             cluster randomized trial;

          -  Weight-for-Height Z-score ≥-3 (WHO Growth Standards 2006) and Mid-Upper Arm
             Circumference ≥115mm without bilateral edema;

          -  Major clinical complications;

          -  Failure to appetite test;

          -  Refuse to participate at the study.
